 <metadata>
  <name>G26-18_Angles_Sant_Dalmai</name>
  <desc>Lollipop route with about 23 km overlap.  5 km to get out of Girona busy roads, 11.5 km to get to loop part of Lollipop.  Loop part features El Mas Llunes descent, unfortunate 6.5 km on C-63 (main road) to get to lovely 7 km segment to Sant Dalmai and 6 km of quiet flatlands to finish loop part.</desc>
